x4freetext: The yield/sample thickness given here should only
be used in the region below ~2 keV. The region above
can be used if required but it does not include energy
dependent correction due to the sample holder and
detector, or the self screening and multiple scatt.
effects. The corrections due to the sample holder
and detecor are no longer available.
